    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for exceptionally tough or hard wood from any of numerous species of trees and shrubs, such as ebony, hornbeam, or acacia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
